<bibRefCitation id="47F9009F0D0D44BB55D3629C7EC7D591" author="Zatwarnicki, T" journalOrPublisher="Annales Zoologici" pageId="112" pageNumber="113" pagination="5 - 51" title="A generic classification of the tribe Discocerinini (Diptera: Ephydridae)." volume="51" year="2001">Zatwarnicki and Mathis 2001</bibRefCitation>
